    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎮 沉浸在怀旧与史诗般的战斗世界中！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FANTASY HEARTS 是经典的现代诠释：拥有老派风格的战术角色扮演游戏氛围、硬核回合制战斗和真正的奇幻魔法。如果你曾经热衷于《最终幻想战略版》、《魔法门英雄传》、《Eador》或《Disciples》，在这里你会感到宾至如归。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/018dc30f40db4a6f3b62e3df61dd6f8d.poster.avif?t=1765143938\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/018dc30f40db4a6f3b62e3df61dd6f8d.webm?t=1765143938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/018dc30f40db4a6f3b62e3df61dd6f8d.mp4?t=1765143938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔥 经典类型的全新演绎</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战术 PvP 战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经过深思熟虑的 PvE 任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >六边形战场</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >激励人心的英雄与阵营</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/92b8917032c1c41bf279a3ccb5c53420.poster.avif?t=1765143938\" width=800 height=574 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/92b8917032c1c41bf279a3ccb5c53420.webm?t=1765143938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/92b8917032c1c41bf279a3ccb5c53420.mp4?t=1765143938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FANTASY HEARTS 的世界由各种族群构成。在我们的宇宙中，人类、野兽、精灵、哥布林和亡灵常常并肩作战。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏹 独一无二的英雄</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建你的队伍，制定战术，组合技能，灵活应对每一场战斗。战斗的胜负取决于角色的选择。你可以在队伍中招募：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精灵</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怪物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哥布林</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >甚至还能复活亡者</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/7f97dc5cbba34072189fa2e6c01ec962.poster.avif?t=1765143938\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/7f97dc5cbba34072189fa2e6c01ec962.webm?t=1765143938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/7f97dc5cbba34072189fa2e6c01ec962.mp4?t=1765143938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💥 与最强者战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建由 4–5 名战士组成的小队，在训练中测试你的策略，然后在竞技场中挑战其他玩家。每场战斗都是一次新的考验，考验的不仅是力量，还有你适应战场环境的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/4a312118ece2f5747460d2da2628bdc9.poster.avif?t=1765143938\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/4a312118ece2f5747460d2da2628bdc9.webm?t=1765143938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/4a312118ece2f5747460d2da2628bdc9.mp4?t=1765143938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🛡️ 自定义你的军队</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战场不只是装饰。地形、掩体和战术位置可能是胜利的关键。谨慎规划每一步——你将获得回报。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/dfcb4661785b2e3477a104afba4278c5.poster.avif?t=1765143938\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/dfcb4661785b2e3477a104afba4278c5.webm?t=1765143938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/dfcb4661785b2e3477a104afba4278c5.mp4?t=1765143938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🤝 公会、活动、社区</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建自己的公会或加入现有公会，参与限时活动，在酒馆完成任务，雇佣雇佣兵，并在怀旧的氛围中与其他玩家交流。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/17ef0df867f6b85f5f1399f83393efa8.poster.avif?t=1765143938\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/17ef0df867f6b85f5f1399f83393efa8.webm?t=1765143938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258090/extras/17ef0df867f6b85f5f1399f83393efa8.mp4?t=1765143938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 Fantasy Hearts 等待它的英雄。加入我们，书写你的传奇。</p>",
